{
  "stem": "27340.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, uh, by, by the time my father was in the concentration camp, m-my mother, who was a very courageous woman and a very assertive lady, literally went to Gestapo headquarters every day to demand her husband's release.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And She tells me, and I think this is very true, although she told it to me, she made such a nuisance of herself in a dignified manner that the Nazis started to gain a considerable amount of respect for her and offered her, for instance, a seat to sit down.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was quite fit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was in her middle 40s at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whereas other women who much older still had to stand up and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They developed some kind of a preferential treatment for her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, uh, she fought like hell to try and get him out of there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, of course, that in itself was of no avail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She also instigated tremendous attempts to various countries, to various embassies, to try and get her small family out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I think Buchenwald, however horrendous it was, even to our family-- and my father survived it, there were lots of people who didn't survive it-- was perhaps a motivator to do something constructive about getting out of there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do remember that at that time h-here in England-- and this is a remarkable story, even by today's standards-- the, uh, an appeal was made to the House of Commons that, uh, one ought to try and save as many children as possible.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it seems incredible by today's standards that that appeal was made a day or two after the Kristallnacht, let's say on the 10th, 11th, or 12th of November.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
